{"tid":2276797,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國大選｜評論：60%選民認為拜登無法完成4年任期 副手賀錦麗更值得關注","createTime":"2020-11-08T04:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T05:02:07.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ea5d6f6ce13557e5e689bfefd799b9c85d458e","tid":2276797,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:47:25.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n美國民主黨總統參選人拜登本月生日後就滿78歲，最近一項民調顯示有近60%受訪者認為他當選也不可能做完四年任期，他的副手賀錦麗有機會繼任總統，令這名副總統人選成為外界最關注的重點。英國作者亞當斯（Guy Adams）撰文指，賀錦麗在眾多熱門議題上立場偏進步派，被特朗普陣營形容是「堅定左派的特洛伊木馬」。<br />\n大選前選民已質疑78歲高齡的拜登即使當選，能否完成四年任期，民調機構「拉斯穆森報告」（Rasmussen Reports）8月公佈的民調顯示，有59%選民認為拜登「可能」不能完成任期，認為「非常有可能」的則有39%。但需留意的是，若以政黨區分，在認為有「可能」的受訪者中，有49%是民主黨選民。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201108/TBCA74L5UBAHBG6HJRGYCKYKX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201108%2FTBCA74L5UBAHBG6HJRGYCKYKX4%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft2%2BzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=c8076d43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201108%2FTBCA74L5UBAHBG6HJRGYCKYKX4%2F&h=8f7317f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201108/TBCA74L5UBAHBG6HJRGYCKYKX4/</a>"},{"pid":"57c44a8fa3fde3e61be014f8a4db5bb279c29210","tid":2276797,"uid":380450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"咁又選佢？ Anything but trump"},{"pid":"e2e64358e85fc37418e401df55ecace4233d3086","tid":2276797,"uid":155095,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:49:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>女人，黑人，亞裔</strong><br />\n<br />\n一次過滿足左膠三個願望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ou2gXEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fou2gXEA.jpg&h=72202937&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e0482b664d10c7d0c40d7a297a00c478fffebf2","tid":2276797,"uid":93649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:51:58.000Z"